{"tid":1335914,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"原來我老細有上連燈，結果我比人炒左。。。","createTime":"2019-07-20T17:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:23:28.000Z","uid":98868,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c22cf16a2aad1c551c14c1dada141215ba6bc195","tid":1335914,"uid":98868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"話說早排返夜撞鬼<br />\n然後開post同各種巴絲打分享<br />\n順便壯下膽 原來我老細都有睇到個post<br />\n跟住第二朝已經問我尋晚有無特別野發生<br />\n佢平時唔會主動問的<br />\n<br />\n到今個月輪到我再去返工<br />\n佢一知係我返 即刻cut我duty<br />\n我問個人事部點解應承左叫我返 又臨時cut個duty<br />\n<br />\n佢比我理由係老細要求搵女人返 唔要男人<br />\n但我返咁耐呢份工從來都無性別要求<br />\n擺明係針對同報復我將公司鬧鬼件事放上連登<br />\n<br />\n我有兩個結論<br />\n1.擺野上連燈要三思<br />\n2.老細(姓chxw)我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f0f8178d3f0747953913c24e48a4bafbe4059a","tid":1335914,"uid":256943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:06:30.000Z","msg":"開名啦 咩公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ff5f581f61326d080386ebcec5b624cec3b9ae","tid":1335914,"uid":98868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"嬲得制 打錯左幾隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c8776f236a9983ceff3577c4803eac6e002117","tid":1335914,"uid":284170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"開名啦 大家識做㗎啦"},{"pid":"cced0d60937937c1767f3df4fe738dd466977dff","tid":1335914,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3de458da396c1f976dbfc43ee7c860739ea691","tid":1335914,"uid":50274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201